##Diary of the 40th about the closure of Milan in autumn

Micro signal

Function introduction, reach consensus, create theory, make route, put forward program, establish principle

Just like after the city was shut down, many netizens began to make their own video diaries, which let the world know about the daily life of people in Wuhan and their many emotions in the face of the epidemic. The 40-day talks are also creating a platform for people in different countries to see the state of people in Italy.

- Introduction to the author -

Cool Autumn, working and living in Milan.

Welcome to Autumn Cool Public Number: Wild Story ID: ye-story

Wild Tomato -- a feminist in Milan, on twitter

The following is a diary of Milan's closure from the 6th to the 8th days of autumn.

Click "read the original Article" to see the wild story.

- DAY 6 -

Easter egg of the day: in the face of the epidemic crisis, optimistic Italians have launched an online campaign. Let's take a look at it. Special thanks to Bologna Lory for sharing!

- DAY 7 -

Today, at the invitation of 4xdecameron, I gave an interview to the Chinese students who were studying in Italy under the epidemic situation.

Talk on the 40th: here is a trick, we will be collected in the following interview to collate, put together to show everyone.

- DAY 8 -

8. Two days at home over the weekend, the sweet sounds of birds interspersed with distant ambulance sirens. The supermarket near my home is basically normal, but access to the supermarket is limited, the restaurant can only take-out, can have Chinese supermarket delivery home is lucky.
